{"tid":2068574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港最大白票黨","createTime":"2020-06-17T19:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:55:25.000Z","uid":38526,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d73bdd67b421b416c66fd2ddc1e6159c2c2cdd21","tid":2068574,"uid":38526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:37:41.000Z","msg":"張舉能獲委任終院首席法官 民主黨將投棄權票<br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）特首林鄭月娥於3月宣佈任命終審法院常任法官張舉能，明年起出任終審法官首席法官。立法會即將就任命作出表決，民主黨表示將投棄權票。民主黨許智峯指，是次投票決定並非取決於張舉能的能力優劣，而是向香港市民及法律界發出警號，表達法治已經危在旦夕。他提醒司法機構應該守護法治及制衡政府，而非配合政府施政。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯提到過去幾年，律政司曾多次提出政治檢控，對親建制及警察案例則採用「包容、不檢討」的態度，與市民期望相距甚遠。他強調法治經已垂危，司法獨立不斷倒退，故希望藉着投票表達香港人對法治的憂慮，重申「破壞法治嘅人必會受到唾棄」。許智峯亦呼籲司法機構應為公義服務，而非為政權服務。<br />\n<br />\n至於張舉能是否出任大法官的適合人選，許指民主黨暫不評論，稱留待日後發展，並期望張舉能以實際行動守護法治及司法獨立。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鍾子希、麥倩怡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074630?fbclid=IwAR3eRzptG189jcAR62rY7rEH2e6g44by24vULOOIpMwE6WyoefCQ0pwBd0M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074630%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3eRzptG189jcAR62rY7rEH2e6g44by24vULOOIpMwE6WyoefCQ0pwBd0M&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=352211c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074630%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3eRzptG189jcAR62rY7rEH2e6g44by24vULOOIpMwE6WyoefCQ0pwBd0M&h=84d71a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074630?fbclid=IwAR3eRzptG189jcAR62rY7rEH2e6g44by24vULOOIpMwE6WyoefCQ0pwBd0M</a>"},{"pid":"5cb86a87610e259978a0efd2da3cfa2dac27c5ea","tid":2068574,"uid":38526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n梁啟智:立會棄權=反對<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/posts/3013978175306165?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkaichil%2Fposts%2F3013978175306165%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=0b0dd40b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/posts/3013978175306165?__tn__=-R</a>"},{"pid":"93f1088f9c471fc71b060b5295f22a4960059cc3","tid":2068574,"uid":38526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:48:04.000Z","msg":"民主黨<br />\nMY香港"},{"pid":"e7fd4524f816a1b310a4c08d416c28e7d54c8f3a","tid":2068574,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"最大白票黨：熱狗"},{"pid":"1bb257ab71350c63bf794ec7461d065f13ee184b","tid":2068574,"uid":131282,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e7fd4524f816a1b310a4c08d416c28e7d54c8f3a","tid":2068574,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"最大白票黨：熱狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:55:08.000Z","msg":"系 睇松泰投票記錄就知佢系大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3197a64cff0572a31ab0482e6a97ea6001bbc9ad","tid":2068574,"uid":38526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bb257ab71350c63bf794ec7461d065f13ee184b","tid":2068574,"uid":131282,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e7fd4524f816a1b310a4c08d416c28e7d54c8f3a","tid":2068574,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"最大白票黨：熱狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:55:08.000Z","msg":"系 睇松泰投票記錄就知佢系大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:59:41.000Z","msg":"1個叫選民投白票<br />\n1個選民投完佢之後入去投白票<br />\n2篤屎<br />\n1個得1個入到去,另1個有7個<br />\n邊篤大D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476ea3bdb9ae3888b0a8c1878b7a9894c04def63","tid":2068574,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:19:02.000Z","msg":"我啱啱搵到15年嘅一篇文, 原來白鴿一直都係反攬炒"},{"pid":"6f361a54b43cf4b33b0affa1975a1f8615b26b57","tid":2068574,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:44:13.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"ed3e1baaa37a8bac685696ad45cac18b0ae660a1","tid":2068574,"uid":38526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"係咪今日投"},{"pid":"ab3e6cb14926bba683cae6e327e48ed1cf864463","tid":2068574,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDEysFk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDEysFk.gif&h=8e491aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zirNFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zirNFt.jpg&h=c6c17ad1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01ac123bd16705f990616c04a1c50e515ecbddf7","tid":2068574,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"又一個熱狗POST"},{"pid":"ab34bb90bf16466afb7112